data.description: Don’t miss out on this lovely maintenance-free 1-level ranch end unit condo that feels like a townhome in a gated community! * Welcomed by vaulted ceilings throughout the entire living room, dining room and kitchen. * Kitchen offers recessed lighting, a spacious pantry, and all stainless steel appliances! * Separate room for laundry. * Accommodating primary bedroom with adjoining bath with a walk-in shower, double sink vanity, and a large walk-in closet. * Attached 2-car garage and driveway! * 2023 New Overhead Door and Overhead Garage Door Opener *Central air * All windows, sliding glass door, wood laminate flooring, and kitchen appliances replaced in 2017 * Walk-out to enjoy the outdoors in the privately enclosed patio. * Located in the peaceful gated community of The Foothills. * Conveniently located near schools, Ft. Carson’s front gates, the World Arena, Highway 115 and I-25! Really close to shopping! * Only 3 minutes away from King Soopers and Starbucks!
